        </itemmetadata>
        <presentation>
          <material>
            <mattext texttype="text/html"><![CDATA[The experimental C-O bond length in CO<sub>3</sub><sup>2-</sup> is 1.28 Å. Given that single bonds are 1.43 Å and double bonds are 1.21 Å, what is the bond order?]]></mattext>
